description:
We are all hungry. Draw inspiration from Ecclesiastes 3:11, and explore how the void and hunger we often feel is often mistakenly attempted to be filled with philosophy, materialism, and secularism. However, these prove inadequate against the soul's true hunger and thirst, which, as Jesus declares, can only be satisfied by Him, the "Bread of Life." The video emphasizes the necessity of Christ, the Bread from Heaven, in sustaining our spiritual life and providing the strength to follow His path. #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jEz3XTESMMA&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=54
